                            <comment id="12548324" author="djd" created="Tue, 4 Dec 2007 17:55:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch that marks an Activation for a dynamic EmbedResultSet as single use to ensure it is closed when the ResultSet is closed.&lt;/p&gt;

